These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: juice, sprite, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
Pet: hamster, goldfish, fish, snake
1. Pet:snake is on the left of Beverage:almond-milk##1
2. Beverage:juice is on the left of Pet:goldfish##1
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:fish is on the left or right of Pet:snake##3
5. Beverage:juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | juice | sprite | hot-chocolate | almond-milk |
| Pet        | hamster | goldfish   | snake | fish    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: thriller, western, mystery, documentary
Nationality: mexican, indian, egyptian, argentine
1. Movie-Genre:western is on the left of Movie-Genre:documentary##1
2. Nationality:mexican is on the left of Nationality:egyptian##1
3. Nationality:egyptian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:mexican == Movie-Genre:thriller##1
5. Nationality:indian is on the right of Nationality:egyptian##1
6. Nationality:mexican == Movie-Genre:thriller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | thriller  | western  | documentary |
| Nationality   | argentine    | mexican | egyptian | indian    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: cherry, plum, potato, cucumber
Movie-Genre: epic, thriller, family, satire
1. Food:cucumber is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:satire##3
2. Food:potato is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:satire is on the left or right of Food:plum##3
4. Movie-Genre:satire is on the right of Movie-Genre:family##1
5. Movie-Genre:epic is in an odd position##4
6. Food:plum is on the right of Food:potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | cucumber | potato | plum    | cherry      |
| Movie-Genre   | family        | satire     | epic | thriller |

