.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: card-games, board-games, sudoku, video-games
Music-Genre: salsa, pop, rock, electronic
1. Hobby:board-games is between Music-Genre:salsa and Music-Genre:electronic##2
2. Hobby:video-games is on the left of Hobby:card-games##1
3. Music-Genre:rock is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:pop is on the left of Music-Genre:electronic##1
5. Music-Genre:pop is on the right of Hobby:card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | video-games | card-games | board-games | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | salsa   | pop    | electronic  |

