.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: fanta, tea, 7up, water
Music-Genre: ambient, r&b, blues, techno
1. Beverage:fanta == Music-Genre:techno##1
2. Music-Genre:ambient is on the right of Beverage:fanta##1
3. Music-Genre:techno is between Music-Genre:ambient and Beverage:7up##2
4. Beverage:fanta is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:techno is on the left or right of Music-Genre:ambient##3
6. Beverage:tea is on the left or right of Music-Genre:r&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea       | 7up   | fanta | water |
| Music-Genre   | blues | r&b | techno        | ambient    |

