.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, lemonade, almond-milk, soy-milk
Food: orange, tomato, blueberry, plum
1. Food:tomato is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:almond-milk is on the left or right of Beverage:hot-chocolate##3
3. Beverage:soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:blueberry is on the left of Food:plum##1
5. Food:plum is on the right of Beverage:hot-chocolate##1
6. Food:blueberry is in an even position##4
7. Food:orange == Beverage:lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | hot-chocolate    | almond-milk       | lemonade |
| Food       | tomato  | blueberry | plum | orange  |

